The paper discusses architecture search for neural models, which is a topic that falls under the broad category of machine learning. Specifically, the paper focuses on continual and multi-task learning, which are subfields of machine learning. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CV (Computer Vision), cs.CL (Computation and Language), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
